OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fcloudy start to the evening, but some
OL,7,Foccasional breaks in the cloud are
OL,8,Flikely to develop later in the night
OL,9,Fwith perhaps a few patches of mist and
OL,10,Ffog developing by dawn. Winds
OL,11,Fgenerally falling light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FVariable cloud around Tuesday
OL,14,Fwith sunny spells, the best of these
OL,15,Fmost likely during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
